column5: Going to Marchington Lakeand I was wondering if anyone had good luck on any of the portage lakes. I know Clamshell and Singapore are good,I'm looking for info on the others.
I'm going up in a few weeks. Plan on hitting Rock and possibly Zarn. Stanzskimi is generally good also. Waterfalls and reefs this time of year will be key.
Super low water out there fellas. Watch yer props!
I'll second that, water is low everywhere, that water system seems to be even more so.
We are going in on Sept 9, when will you be there? wmd
The week leading into Labor Day. I'll try to get a report out when I get back.
